channel.title: Webclient or Regular Client
channel.description: So I made this beatiful server with a client to go with it. I was also planning on putting my server on rsps-hq.com but they are down now. So I go to my client and it got corrupted somehow. So my base is Project Insanity. I need someone to direct me to a place to get a good client or help me in TV to get everything in the client to match my server. And if there are any Weblcient makers I would love to know because the one I wanted to use is now gone. Thanks, Tyler
